                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 624.) I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> The prosecutor laid hold of two of us; the other one pulled from him and ran away, and he took me.</p>
